Set Usage Tests
===============

Set and use in condition:
{{set threshold = 5}}
{{set myvalue = @(intvalue10)}}
{{if @(myvalue > threshold)}}Value {{:myvalue}} exceeds threshold {{:threshold}}{{endif}}

Set computed value and reuse:
{{set base = @(intvalue10 * 2)}}
{{set doubled = @(base * 2)}}
base = {{:base}}, doubled = {{:doubled}}

Override existing value:
{{set counter = 1}}
counter = {{:counter}}
{{set counter = 2}}
counter = {{:counter}}

